です。<br>UXリサーチのご経験がない方も、はじめに簡単な講義があるのでご安心ください。また、ゲームプレイ後にはリフレクションを通して、皆さんと学びを深めましょう。はじめてUXリサーチを学ぶ方、中でも「楽しみながら」学びたい方にオススメです。<br>「たのしい！リサーチャーすごろく」についてはこちらのnoteをご参照ください。<br>https://note.com/zkmymkz/n/n7438131d88f9","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"@mobile":{"fontSize":"12px"},"color":"#FFFFFF","flex":"none","fontFamily":"var(--s-font-b480a875)","fontSize":"14px","fontWeight":700,"height":"auto","letterSpacing":"0.06em","lineHeight":"2","margin":"0px 0px 24px 0px","textAlign":"left","width":"100%"},"tagName":"","uuid":"736e5c9d-5ab8-47a2-a542-82c4990c3c4e","children":[]},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"content":{"data":"申し込む","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"@mobile":{"fontSize":"16px"},"color":"#FFFFFF","flex":"none","fontFamily":"var(--s-font-b480a875)","fontSize":"18px","fontWeight":700,"height":"auto","letterSpacing":"0.06em","lineHeight":"normal","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","textAlign":"left","width":"auto"},"tagName":"","uuid":"34a5a9c5-d2c2-449c-97c3-79053082b085","children":[]}],"link":{"newTab":true,"path":"https://designship2023-workshop1.peatix.com/"},"name":"Box","style":{"@mobile":{"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","padding":"8px 32px 8px 32px"},"alignContent":"center","alignItems":"center","background":"#da297b","borderRadius":"48px","flex":"none","flexDirection":"column","flexWrap":"nowrap","height":"auto","justifyContent":"center","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","padding":"8px 40px 8px 40px","width":"auto"},"tagName":"","uuid":"1ee12712-0c2b-4340-957f-df29165ac86e"}],"name":"<group>","style":{"@mobile":{"alignContent":"center","alignItems":"center","flexDirection":"column","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center"},"alignContent":"center","alignItems":"center","flexDirection":"row","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"center","margin":"0px 16px 0px 0px","padding":"0px"},"tagName":"div","uuid":"1c6dd9a1-d004-409c-b807-d8a56333be66"},{"content":{"data":"チケットは完売しました","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"@mobile":{"fontSize":"10px"},"color":"#F